Name: Rose Carte Finale
Desc: Tosses a bouquet of cards into the air. The cards fall and penetrate the ground, inflicting continuous damage on enemies without being affected by enemies in the Damage Reflection status.

H.Old:
MP Cost: 200. Attacks 15 enemies in one screen at 700% Damage 6 times. Attacks 6 enemies around the cards twice at 200% Damage for 8 seconds.
Cooldown: 30 sec
H.New:
MP Cost: 200. Attacks up to 15 enemies at 700% Damage 6 times.
Afterward, the cards stuck in the ground attack up to 6 enemies at 200% Damage 2 times for 8 sec.
Cooldown: 30 sec.
